quoteText: At the top of our Website Privacy Policy, we will indicate the date of the most recent update to this Website Privacy Policy. Where required by applicable law, we will apply changes only after notifying and/or obtaining your consent before any material changes to our Website Privacy Policy apply to you.
title: The service may change its terms at any time, but the user will receive notification of the changes.
